 很多同学以为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bigcup_{\alpha\in I}(G_{\alpha}-E_{\alpha})=\bigcup_{\alpha\in I}G_{\alpha}-\bigcup_{\alpha\in I}E_{\alpha},\quad\text{或以为}\quad\bigcup_{\alpha\in I}(G_{\alpha}-E_{\alpha})=\bigcup_{\alpha\in I}G_{\alpha}-\bigcap_{\alpha\in I}E_{\alpha}.
