 正解是: 设
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bigcup_{\alpha\in I}U_{\alpha}=\bigcup_{\alpha\in I}(G_{\alpha}-E_{\alpha})=\bigcup_{\alpha\in I}G_{\alpha}-A,
\]

\end_inset

